  "texts": [
    "While commonly referred to as '武王伐纣 (King Wu attacked Zhou)', there are various textual variations of this event.",
    "Since the system has built-in millions of text reuse pairs, the enhanced browsing module allows users to find sentence reuses and variations across various literary works.",
    "In this section, we used this module to investigate the variants of this allusion.",
    "We gathered three frequently used phrases (武王伐纣,武王克殷,武王克商), consolidated similar texts, and removed irrelevant ones.",
    "As a result, we obtained 281 texts describing the event, with 48 main variations and the frequency distribution is illustrated in Fig. 10a."
